column2: The creature is ornery. It ignores your command.
Intelligence Report: Palawa Joko I Page 01[s]

Legendary Renegade. Summon Lieutenant Ofela Soulcleave to grant your allies' strikes incredible bloodthirst, inflicting damage and restoring health.
Lieutenant Soulcleave can only empower players.
You cannot use this item while transformed.
Intelligence Report: Palawa Joko I Page 06[s]
Found only in Black Lion Chests during specific times of the year.
Eyes like fire, wings like smoke. What does your heart desire, what does your soul invoke?
Throw an axe to cripple your foe.
The creature is focused on you, but it still seems confused.

Intelligence Report: Palawa Joko I Page 04[s]
Travel to the Crystal Desert and confront the rampaging war god, Balthazar.
Push back foes and projectiles with a hot-air blast, burning foes that are already on fire.
